

Lingua::EN::Gender


Small module for inflecting pronouns for a bunch of different
genders.

Genders currently supported are:
   neuter
   male
   female
   either
   spivak
   splat
   plural
   egotistical
   royal
   2nd
   sie/hir
   zie/zir


INSTALLING
==========

After unzipping and untarring the distribution directory, you install
the library by running these commands:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


